reviewText: This edition of guys gone wild features all military men. Now yes not all show full nudity but you do see several cute marine butts and some huge military guns. Not a bad dvd. Keep in mind these are guys you would never see nude otherwise.

They should rename this franchise "Guys Gone Mild", because this DVD was mostly boring. The better looking guys didn't show the "goods", but the worst looking guys did. WTF? That's not to say that any of these guys were ugly, they just didn't float my boat. I think this might be my last Guys Gone Wild DVD.
